high_descs: Turn around, walk forward to counter, turn left, walk forward to counter
Put tomato inside microwave, close microwave, turn on, open and remove tomato, close microwave
Turn left, walk forward, turn left near end of kitchen island
Put tomato on top of kitchen island
anns.task_desc: Take tomato from counter to microwave, place on kitchen island

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the microwave
Pick up the tomato from the counter right of the microwave
Look slightly down to face toward the microwave
Cook the tomato in the microwave then remove it
Turn left and walk a few feet before turning left to face the kitchen island
Put the tomato down on the kitchen island
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked tomato on the kitchen island

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the counter, then hang a left and walk up to the microwave.
Pick up the tomato off of the counter to the right of the microwave.
Look down at the microwave on the counter.
Put the tomato in the microwave and close the door then turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds take the tomato out and close the microwave.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the kitchen island.
Put the heated tomato on the kitchen island to the right of the closest loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato on the kitchen island.
